author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Temasek Takes Share Stake In Boeing, Cuts Share Stake in BofA
text:
Feb 14 (Reuters) - Temasek Holdings (Private) Ltd:
* TAKES SHARE STAKE OF 525,636 SHARES IN BOEING - SEC FILING
* REPORTS SHARE STAKE OF 5.6 MILLION SHARES IN DOWDUPONT - SEC FILING
* CUTS SHARE STAKE IN BANK OF AMERICA BY 33.3 PERCENT TO 532,082 SHARES - SEC FILING
* CHANGE IN HOLDINGS ARE AS OF DEC. 31, 2017 AND COMPARED WITH PREVIOUS QUARTER ENDED SEPT. 30, 2017 Source text for quarter ended Dec 31, 2017: ( bit.ly/2EpcSgh ) Source text for quarter ended Sept 30, 2017: ( bit.ly/2yBi2ic )
